ia/HJhtVhYWEAAFNQx.jpg", "height": 562}], "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 480, "created": 1780100521000, "id": "2060517047755264345", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1601768744669282304/S-WFCxAC_normal.jpg", "displayName": "The General", "username": "GeneralMCNews"}, "content": "BREAKING: Congress is attempting to fuse the U.S. military with Israel's as Section 224 of the 2027 National Defense Authorization Act \"would all but fuse American and Israeli armed forces together\"", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 1484}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsduW2bN", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 392, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8647385, "raw_content": "Never be afraid to LOSE.\nThere is no reward in life without risk or effort.\n\nWhen you play a new video game what happens at first?\n\nYou die over and over and learn.. You get better. You die less frequently.\n\nEventually you get better and even master the game to become one of the best.\n\nLife works the same way.\n\nAll you have to do is make sure you are playing the right game, and keep getting better. There is no failure. Just a graph of you getting better at life!!\n\nDo not give up, do not surrender, do not listen to weaker people. You want something, there is always a price. Master yourself and your skills and do not ever let the noise or weakness of emotions like fear and doubt stop you!\n\nGET AFTER IT! ", "author": "HeNotMedicated", "created": 1780080290476, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "HeNotMedicated", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhas